- content_for :title, "Terms and Conditions"
- content_for :meta_description, "Read the Nilam Invoice terms and conditions for acceptable use, account responsibilities, billing access, plan usage, and service limitations."

.page-hero.page-hero--tight
  .page-hero__content
    %span.eyebrow Legal
    %h1.page-title Terms and Conditions
    %p.page-subtitle These terms and conditions explain the basic rules for using Nilam Invoice, including account access, acceptable use, billing features, plan access, and service limitations.
  .page-hero__panel
    %span.hero-pill Important
    %p.mb-2 By using Nilam Invoice, you agree to follow these terms.
    %p.mb-0 If you do not agree, you should stop using the service.

.page-section.page-section--features
  .feature-list.feature-list--enhanced
    .meta-item.meta-item--accent
      %span.meta-label Use of service
      %span.meta-value You agree to use the platform only for lawful business purposes and to keep your login credentials secure.
    .meta-item.meta-item--accent
      %span.meta-label Account responsibility
      %span.meta-value You are responsible for the invoice data, customer information, and business records created under your account.
    .meta-item.meta-item--accent
      %span.meta-label Plan access
      %span.meta-value Access to certain features may depend on the plan you purchase, renew, or maintain in active status.

.page-section.page-section--plans
  .section-heading
    %div
      %span.eyebrow Core terms
      %h2.section-title Main conditions of use
      %p.muted.mb-0 These terms provide a simple operating framework for the app.
  .card.stack
    %div
      %h3.card-title Acceptable use
      %p.muted.mb-0 You must not misuse the service, attempt unauthorized access, interfere with system operation, or use the platform for fraudulent or illegal billing activity.
    %div
      %h3.card-title Data and accuracy
      %p.muted.mb-0 Nilam Invoice provides tools for invoice generation and reporting, but you remain responsible for reviewing invoice accuracy, tax treatment, and business compliance.
    %div
      %h3.card-title Payments and renewals
      %p.muted.mb-0 Paid features, invoice limits, Excel exports, and renewal availability may change based on the plan assigned to your account and its current status.
    %div
      %h3.card-title Availability
      %p.muted.mb-0 We may update, improve, suspend, or limit parts of the service when needed for maintenance, security, or product changes.
    %div
      %h3.card-title Limitation
      %p.muted.mb-0 The service is provided on an ongoing basis without a guarantee that it will be uninterrupted or error-free in every situation.
    %div
      %h3.card-title Updates to terms
      %p.muted.mb-0 These terms may be updated over time. Continued use of the platform after updates means you accept the revised terms.
